qHttpd Changes
--------------

[v1.2.8]
o Close loger fd before termination
o Change getopt arg 'v' -> 'V'.
o Adjust to print out informational messages to stdout.
o Add response200()
o change local time format to GMT time format.
o add lua script function: boolean response:setCode().
o improve that response-hook is always called before sending response.
o some prototype changes in http_response.c
o improve connection-ignoring handler

[v1.2.6]
o Support HTTP Basic Authentication Programming Module (refer http_auth.c)
o Support Virtual Host (refer hook.c)
o Support AutoConf
o Performance improvements

[v1.2.4]
o Support HTTP extentions for WebDAV
  AllowedMethods = OPTIONS,HEAD,GET,PUT,PROPFIND,PROPPATCH,MKCOL,MOVE,DELETE,LOCK,UNLOCK

[v1.2.3]
o Support PUT, DELETE methods
o control allowed methods.
  [configuration file]
  AllowedMethods = OPTIONS,HEAD,GET,PUT,DELETE
o Bug fixes

[v1.2.0]
o Embedded LUA script engine.
  see conf/qhttpd.lua.dist
  [configuration file]
  qhttpd.EnableLua = NO
  qhttpd.LuaScript = ${qhttpd.ConfDir}/qhttpd.lua
